{"tid":1159061,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Dr Strange夠唔夠Endgame Thanos打？","createTime":"2019-05-17T11:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T12:01:11.000Z","uid":73952,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"88a49efbc9d8e4a678bcca8f6b9931ff603ae371","tid":1159061,"uid":73952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夠<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔夠<br />\n<br />\n好似冇乜點討論過<br />\n個人認為夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIW已經同四石Thanos過招<br />\nEndgame Thanos得套甲同把刀<br />\n應該頂唔到Dr Strange d招<br />\n分分鐘再出影分身/鏡像已經輕鬆KO Thanos<br />\n所以Marvel先要安排佢玩水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家點睇？"},{"pid":"ceb3fa3f41ffd683d43641a9d005a6514935b47d","tid":1159061,"uid":73952,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RhYeuOH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRhYeuOH.gif&h=c59b3226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇石點樣解呢招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf0436e485fd8c25ee5bb90c57f3d0d618750de","tid":1159061,"uid":235174,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:01:11.000Z","msg":"如果按角色技能黎睇，淨係用portal都可以切開Thanos或者丟佢去外太空<br />\n<br />\nd外國影評人話，Infinity War入面Thanos明明有威力強大既手套識得出技能，又power stone又time stone，響外星果段比幾個人夾手差d ko佢，最尾重要比Thor插左一野<br />\n<br />\n響Endgame入面Thanos明明冇手套，多塊爛鬼刀，面對更多英雄，比三王夾擊都可以打極都唔死，到最後要逼Ironman同歸於盡<br />\n<br />\n但結論係大家真係唔好諗太多<br />\n其實同龍珠一樣，power level隨住劇情須要增強減弱，目標都係為左達成一個epic ending送兩個主角一程"}]}